    <item>
      <title>反向套利交易看到美元押注由新兴市场货币资助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/carry-trade-gets-turned-on-its-head-stoking-rush-to-the-dollar</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几十年来，套利交易者以低利率借入美元，投资于收益较高的新兴市场货币。但现在这种趋势正在发生逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/carry-trade-gets-turned-on-its-head-stoking-rush-to-the-dollar</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 12:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>消息人士称，埃利奥特持有巴菲特青睐的住友商事“大量”股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位知情人士透露，埃利奥特管理公司(Elliott Management Corp.)已持有住友商事株式会社(Sumitomo Corp.)的“大量”股份，住友商事株式会社是沃伦·巴菲特最喜欢的日本贸易公司之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-28/elliott-said-to-build-large-stake-in-buffett-favored-sumitomo</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 28 Apr 2024 09:49:48 GMT</pubDate>
